    },
    {
      "start": 605.68,
      "end": 607.26,
      "text": "네, 이 장면 다시 한번 들어볼게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 607.26,
      "end": 610.3,
      "text": "When we were little, I used to see you guys in town."
