      "end": 839.39,
      "text": "Lucy Goosey."
    },
    {
      "start": 839.39,
      "end": 840.39,
      "text": "라는 표현이 재미있는데요."
    },
    {
      "start": 840.53,
      "end": 841.25,
      "text": "Lucy Goosey."
    },
    {
      "start": 841.33,
      "end": 841.55,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 841.63,
      "end": 842.07,
      "text": "괜찮죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 842.29,
      "end": 842.51,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 842.75,
      "end": 844.91,
      "text": "약간 만약에 누군가가"
    },
    {
      "start": 844.91,
      "end": 846.93,
      "text": "Overprotected by parents."
    },
    {
      "start": 847.29,
      "end": 847.51,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 847.65,
      "end": 848.49,
      "text": "그런 상황에서"
    },
    {
      "start": 848.49,
      "end": 850.41,
      "text": "Lucy Boosey 이렇게 쓰나요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 850.59,
      "end": 851.19,
      "text": "Lucy Goosey."
    },
    {
      "start": 851.21,
      "end": 851.99,
      "text": "Lucy Goosey."
    },
    {
      "start": 852.33,
      "end": 853.45,
      "text": "If you're overprotective,"
    },
    {
      "start": 853.65,
      "end": 854.89,
      "text": "you're not Lucy Goosey."
    },
    {
      "start": 855.23,
      "end": 856.33,
      "text": "Lucy Goosey is"
    },
    {
      "start": 856.33,
      "end": 858.01,
      "text": "You can do whatever you want."
    },
    {
      "start": 858.01,
      "end": 859.17,
      "text": "그냥 냅두는 거."
    },
    {
      "start": 859.31,
      "end": 861.03,
      "text": "You can do whatever you want."
    },
    {
      "start": 861.13,
      "end": 863.13,
      "text": "I'm not going to tell you to do anything."
    },
    {
      "start": 863.21,
      "end": 864.33,
      "text": "다 한대적인 상황이었네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 864.69,
      "end": 864.91,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 865.23,
      "end": 866.75,
      "text": "So maybe Ruby's parents"
    },
    {
      "start": 866.75,
      "end": 867.05,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 867.15,
      "end": 868.17,
      "text": "Or more Lucy Goosey."
    },
    {
      "start": 868.21,
      "end": 868.93,
      "text": "Lucy Goosey."
    },
    {
      "start": 868.97,
      "end": 870.31,
      "text": "Miles' parents are strict."
    },
    {
      "start": 870.43,
      "end": 870.73,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 870.95,
      "end": 871.51,
      "text": "Overprotective."
    },
    {
      "start": 871.53,
      "end": 872.45,
      "text": "저 같은 경우는요."
    },
    {
      "start": 872.49,
      "end": 874.79,
      "text": "Miles하고 좀 similar한 상황이에요."
    },
    {
      "start": 875.03,
      "end": 875.33,
      "text": "Oh."
    },
    {
      "start": 875.51,
      "end": 877.39,
      "text": "저희 parents도 also"
    },
    {
      "start": 877.39,
      "end": 879.53,
      "text": "wouldn't let me ride a bus by myself."
    },
    {
      "start": 879.61,
      "end": 880.67,
      "text": "They were very protective."
    },
    {
      "start": 880.67,
      "end": 881.11,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 881.29,
      "end": 881.99,
      "text": "And I wouldn't"
    },
    {
      "start": 881.99,
      "end": 884.73,
      "text": "They wouldn't even let me"
    },
    {
      "start": 884.73,
      "end": 886.99,
      "text": "walk alone the street."
    },
    {
      "start": 887.27,
      "end": 887.29,
      "text": "Oh."
    },
    {
      "start": 887.29,
      "end": 887.71,
      "text": "Really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 887.71,
      "end": 888.71,
      "text": "In Korea,"
    },
    {
      "start": 888.83,
      "end": 889.95,
      "text": "many kids walk alone"
    },
    {
      "start": 889.95,
      "end": 890.69,
      "text": "on the streets."
    },
    {
      "start": 890.79,
      "end": 891.13,
      "text": "Oh, 그래요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 891.43,
      "end": 891.71,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 891.93,
      "end": 893.19,
      "text": "The streets are safe."
    },
    {
      "start": 893.41,
      "end": 894.97,
      "text": "So my niece,"
    },
    {
      "start": 895.15,
      "end": 896.71,
      "text": "she walks all the way to school,"
    },
    {
      "start": 896.83,
      "end": 897.91,
      "text": "which is like"
    },
    {
      "start": 897.91,
      "end": 898.45,
      "text": "five,"
    },
    {
      "start": 898.73,
      "end": 899.79,
      "text": "ten minutes away."
    },
    {
      "start": 900.07,
      "end": 901.29,
      "text": "5분, 10분 거리는"
    },
    {
      "start": 901.29,
      "end": 902.01,
      "text": "그냥 혼자서"
    },
    {
      "start": 902.01,
      "end": 903.43,
      "text": "걷게끔 하시는군요."
    },
    {
      "start": 903.51,
      "end": 904.75,
      "text": "She's in elementary school."
    },
    {
      "start": 904.87,
      "end": 905.63,
      "text": "초등학생인데."
    },
    {
      "start": 905.77,
      "end": 907.25,
      "text": "My mom would never let me do that."
    },
    {
      "start": 907.43,
      "end": 908.87,
      "text": "My mom was more strict."
    },
    {
      "start": 909.05,
      "end": 910.51,
      "text": "Oh, 그러셨군요."
    },
    {
      "start": 910.53,
      "end": 912.59,
      "text": "But your parents were strict, huh?"
    },
    {
      "start": 912.59,
      "end": 912.91,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 912.91,
      "end": 914.27,
      "text": "그래서 they always came"
    },
    {
      "start": 914.27,
      "end": 915.49,
      "text": "to pick me up."
    },
    {
      "start": 916.28,
      "end": 916.72,
      "text": "Oh."
    },
    {
      "start": 917.28,
      "end": 918.64,
      "text": "항상 저를 데리러 오시고"
    },
    {
      "start": 918.64,
      "end": 919.34,
      "text": "태우러 오시고"
    },
    {
      "start": 919.34,
      "end": 920.14,
      "text": "막 그랬었는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 920.14,
      "end": 921.28,
      "text": "아무튼 저는"
    },
    {
      "start": 921.28,
      "end": 921.88,
      "text": "그 당시에"
    },
    {
      "start": 921.88,
      "end": 922.96,
      "text": "제가 너무"
    },
    {
      "start": 922.96,
      "end": 924.76,
      "text": "too overprotected 된다라는"
    },
    {
      "start": 924.76,
      "end": 925.38,
      "text": "생각 때문에"
    },
    {
      "start": 925.38,
      "end": 926.04,
      "text": "좀 싫기도 했었지만"
    },
    {
      "start": 926.04,
      "end": 928.88,
      "text": "Now, yes, thank you."
    },
    {
      "start": 928.98,
      "end": 929.68,
      "text": "Mom and Dad"
    },
    {
      "start": 929.68,
      "end": 930.92,
      "text": "이렇게 전해드리고 싶네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 930.96,
      "end": 931.52,
      "text": "You're thankful."
    },
    {
      "start": 931.84,
      "end": 932.06,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 932.62,
      "end": 933.18,
      "text": "Why?"
    },
    {
      "start": 934.06,
      "end": 935.1,
      "text": "안전하게 잘"
    },
    {
      "start": 935.1,
      "end": 936.5,
      "text": "여태까지 이렇게 잘"
    },
    {
      "start": 936.5,
      "end": 938.1,
      "text": "있게 해주셨을 때."
    },
    {
      "start": 938.12,
      "end": 938.76,
      "text": "그럼요."
    },
    {
      "start": 939.3,
      "end": 939.96,
      "text": "네, 그럼요."
    },
    {
      "start": 940.24,
      "end": 940.84,
      "text": "아무튼."
    },
    {
      "start": 940.9,
      "end": 941.58,
      "text": "부모님 최고죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 941.72,
      "end": 942.68,
      "text": "이 장면"
    },
    {
      "start": 942.68,
      "end": 943.58,
      "text": "한 번 더 들어보겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 944.72,
      "end": 945.34,
      "text": "When we were little,"
    },
    {
      "start": 945.46,
      "end": 946.96,
      "text": "I used to see you guys in town."
    },
    {
      "start": 947.4,
      "end": 947.66,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 948.5,
      "end": 949.36,
      "text": "We were hard to miss."
    },
    {
      "start": 949.9,
      "end": 950.6,
      "text": "There was this one time"
    },
    {
      "start": 950.6,
      "end": 951.32,
      "text": "I think it was like"
    },
    {
      "start": 951.32,
      "end": 953.01,
      "text": "third grade."
    },
    {
      "start": 953.71,
      "end": 954.51,
      "text": "You were at the"
    },
    {
      "start": 954.51,
      "end": 955.09,
      "text": "Seatport Grill"
    },
    {
      "start": 955.09,
      "end": 956.07,
      "text": "and you were ordering"
    },
    {
      "start": 956.07,
      "end": 956.77,
      "text": "for your parents"
    },
    {
      "start": 956.77,
      "end": 958.89,
      "text": "and you were talking"
    },
    {
      "start": 958.89,
      "end": 959.27,
      "text": "to the Whiter"
    },
    {
      "start": 959.27,
      "end": 960.27,
      "text": "like a total baller"
    },
    {
      "start": 960.27,
      "end": 962.0,
      "text": "and then you ordered"
    },
    {
      "start": 962.0,
      "end": 962.6,
      "text": "two beers."
    },
    {
      "start": 963.51,
      "end": 964.65,
      "text": "I thought it was so cool."
    },
    {
      "start": 965.09,
      "end": 965.39,
      "text": "Really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 966.19,
      "end": 966.49,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 967.61,
      "end": 968.37,
      "text": "My parents wouldn't even"
    },
    {
      "start": 968.37,
      "end": 968.99,
      "text": "let me ride the bus"
    },
    {
      "start": 968.99,
      "end": 969.55,
      "text": "by myself."
    },
    {
      "start": 970.89,
      "end": 972.09,
      "text": "이 지혜님께서"
    },
    {
      "start": 972.09,
      "end": 973.97,
      "text": "크리스쌤이 노래도 하는"
    },
    {
      "start": 973.97,
      "end": 975.77,
      "text": "어메이징한 G&B"
    },
    {
      "start": 975.77,
      "end": 977.47,
      "text": "갑자기 노래 언제 했나요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 977.63,
      "end": 979.45,
      "text": "City of stars"
    },
    {
      "start": 979.45,
      "end": 981.37,
      "text": "Oh my, please."
    },
    {
      "start": 981.67,
      "end": 982.85,
      "text": "갑자기 옆에서 막"
    },
    {
      "start": 982.85,
      "end": 983.99,
      "text": "무슨 말인지"
    },
    {
      "start": 983.99,
      "end": 985.07,
      "text": "못 알아듣겠어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 985.07,
      "end": 986.21,
      "text": "막 이러는 경우도"
    },
    {
      "start": 986.21,
      "end": 986.91,
      "text": "생기지 않나요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 987.09,
      "end": 988.19,
      "text": "City of stars"
    },
    {
      "start": 988.19,
      "end": 988.67,
      "text": "할 때"
    },
    {
      "start": 988.67,
      "end": 990.17,
      "text": "아무튼"
    },
    {
      "start": 990.17,
      "end": 990.97,
      "text": "What are you saying?"
    },
    {
      "start": 991.13,
      "end": 991.55,
      "text": "아, 네."
    },
    {
      "start": 991.67,
      "end": 992.61,
      "text": "나중에 설명을 드릴게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 992.83,
      "end": 993.17,
      "text": "Oh my."
    },
    {
      "start": 993.49,
      "end": 994.41,
      "text": "자, 오늘 스크린"
    },
    {
      "start": 994.41,
      "end": 995.03,
      "text": "잉글리쉬는"
    },
    {
      "start": 995.03,
      "end": 995.95,
      "text": "여기까지입니다."
    }
  ]
}